title: O'Neill World Cup Minute - Day 01
description: After three consecutive Lay Days for the O'Neill World Cup of Surfing there appears to be a bump in swell scheduled for Wednesday. Here's a recap of Day 1 action to get you ready for the next time the World Cup runs.
